            <title><![CDATA[Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba – The Hinokami Chronicles 2 DLC character Shinobu Kocho (Infinity Castle) launches April 17]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/04/demon-slayer-kimetsu-no-yaiba-the-hinokami-chronicles-2-dlc-character-shinobu-kocho-infinity-castle-launches-april-17</link>
