            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PS4</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Sixth "Infinity Castle - Part 1 Character Pass" fighter dated.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><em><a title="Games > Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba - The Hinokami Chronicles 2 [19 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/demon-slayer-kimetsu-no-yaiba-the-hinokami-chronicles-2">Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba – The Hinokami Chronicles 2</a></em> downloadable content character Shinobu Kocho (<em>Infinity Castle</em>) will launch on April 17, publisher <a title="Companies > Aniplex [300 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/sony-group-corporation/sony-music-entertainment-japan/aniplex">Aniplex</a> and developer <a title="Companies > CyberConnect2 [631 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/cyberconnect2">CyberConnect2</a> announced. <span id="more-1040208"></span></p><p>Shinobu Kocho (<em>Infinity Castle</em>) can be purchased individually via the “Shinobu Kocho (<em>Infinity Castle</em>) Character Pack,” or as part of the “<em>Infinity Castle</em> – Part 1 Character Pass,” which includes access to <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/09/demon-slayer-kimetsu-no-yaiba-the-hinokami-chronicles-2-adds-muzan-kibutsuji-via-free-update-on-september-18-dlc-infinity-castle-part-1-character-pass-detailed">multiple other characters</a>.</p><p><em>Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba – The Hinokami Chronicles 2</em> is available now for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,514 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,796 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,737 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox One [14,418 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [18,382 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2928600/Demon_Slayer_Kimetsu_no_Yaiba_The_Hinokami_Chronicles_2/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>.</p><p>Watch a new trailer below.</p><h2><span>DLC Character Shinobu Kocho (<em>Infinity Castle</em>) Trailer</span></h2><p><iframe title="家庭用ゲーム「鬼滅の刃 ヒノカミ血風譚2」「胡蝶しのぶ(無限城編)」キャラクターパック紹介映像" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/whJi2Fc41wQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><!-- AD: content -->
